{{!-- Team
================================================== --}}
<div class="docs-section">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1 id="team">Core team</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="lead">{{titleize site.title}} is maintained by a group of invaluable core contributors, with the massive support and involvement of our community. No one person is in charge and everyone has their own areas and donates the time they can afford. In alphabetical order:</p>
  <div class="list-group team">

    {{! Generated from data/team.yml }}
    {{#each team}}
    <div class="list-group-item">
      <iframe class="github-btn" src="{{{follow}}}"></iframe>
      <a class="team-member" href="https://github.com/{{{username}}}">
        <img src="{{{gravatar}}}" alt="@{{{username}}}">
        <strong>{{{name}}}</strong> <small>@{{{username}}}</small>
      </a>
    </div>
    {{/each}}

  </div>
  <p>Get involved with {{titleize site.title}} development by <a href="{{ _assemble.issues }}/new">opening an issue</a> or submitting a pull request (if it's a feature request, please open an issue first). </p>
  <p>Read our <a href="{{ _assemble.master }}CONTRIBUTING.md">contributing guidelines</a> and the <a href="{{resolve 'contributing'}}">developing section</a> of our usage page.</p>
</div>


